  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high.",
    "Add the onion, ginger, and green chili, and stir-fry until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the rice and stir-fry until the rice is lightly toasted.",
    "Add the lemon juice, lemon zest, chicken broth, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover.",
    "Simmer for 5 minutes, or until the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Remove the skillet from the heat and stir in the chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve the citrusy Saudi-Arabian lemon fried rice hot."
